--------------------------------------------------------------------------

Optimized .gitignore for Python / NLP / Jupyter Notebook Projects

--------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Byte-compiled / optimal / internal files

############################################
pycache/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python
env/
venv/
*.egg-info

2. Operating System Files

############################################
.DS_Store
.ipynb_checkpoints  # Jupyter Notebook checkpoints

3. Model Outputs (CRITICAL for large NLP repos)

############################################

Model artifacts saved by the trainer (DistilBERT is large!)

results/
sentiment_model/
*.joblib
*.pkl
*.model
*.pt
*.bin
model_weights.h5

4. Data Files / API Keys

############################################

Dataset files downloaded by the notebook

dataset/
*.csv  # Exclude downloaded or created CSVs
*.zip  # Exclude downloaded zip files
kaggle.json  # Sensitive API key for Kaggle download
